PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - An attempt is made to correct certain conceptual and methodological errors contained in a previous article on the Miner Sentence Completion Scale (MSCS). New data bearing on scorer reliability, construct validity, and multiple choice procedures are introduced. Taken as a whole, the data argue strongly for the psychometric soundness of the MSCS and support its continued use.
AB  - An attempt is made to correct certain conceptual and methodological errors contained in a previous article on the Miner Sentence Completion Scale (MSCS). New data bearing on scorer reliability, construct validity, and multiple choice procedures are introduced. Taken as a whole, the data argue strongly for the psychometric soundness of the MSCS and support its continued use.
